sql: SELECT h.Weight FROM cars_data AS h WHERE h.Weight = 91 AND Weight = (SELECT MAX(Weight) FROM cars_data AS b)
SELECT ContId, ContId FROM continents WHERE  ContId < 7 AND ContId NOT IN (SELECT ContId FROM continents AS b WHERE  b.ContId != 98 LIMIT 8)

SELECT MIN(car_names.MakeId), cars_data.Id, car_names.Model FROM cars_data JOIN car_names ON cars_data.Id = car_names.MakeId JOIN car_makers ON car_names.Make = car_makers.Maker JOIN model_list ON model_list.Maker = car_makers.Id AND car_names.Model = model_list.Model WHERE cars_data.Id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM car_makers AS c WHERE  c.Id >= 68 AND model_list.ModelId = c.Id LIMIT 5) GROUP BY car_names.Model ORDER BY cars_data.Id ASC

SELECT model_list.Model FROM car_names INNER JOIN model_list ON car_names.Model = model_list.Model INNER JOIN car_makers ON model_list.Maker = car_makers.Id AND car_names.MakeId = car_makers.Id WHERE model_list.ModelId > 4 ORDER BY model_list.Model ASC
SELECT CountryName FROM countries WHERE Continent NOT IN (1, 10) AND CountryId != 65 ORDER BY CountryName DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT CountryName), COUNT(DISTINCT Continent), CountryName FROM countries WHERE Continent = 28 AND CountryName NOT IN (SELECT CountryName FROM countries AS s WHERE s.CountryId < 46) GROUP BY CountryName HAVING MAX(CountryId) > 57 ORDER BY CountryName DESC
SELECT Id, Maker FROM car_makers WHERE Maker = 47
SELECT m.MakeId, m.Model FROM car_names AS m WHERE  m.MakeId >= 31 GROUP BY m.Model HAVING SUM(m.MakeId) > 54
SELECT c.Horsepower FROM car_names AS n JOIN cars_data AS c ON c.Id = n.MakeId WHERE c.Accelerate > 59
SELECT AVG(MakeId), COUNT(DISTINCT Model) FROM car_names WHERE MakeId BETWEEN 1 AND 10;

SELECT T1.CountryName AS Country FROM countries AS T1 JOIN car_makers AS T2 ON T1.CountryId = T2.Country JOIN model_list AS T3 ON T2.Id = T3.Maker JOIN car_names AS T4 ON T3.Model = T4.Model WHERE T4.MakeId >= 87 ORDER BY T1.CountryName ASC;
SELECT f.ContId, f.Continent FROM continents AS f WHERE  f.ContId >= 4 OR f.ContId IN (SELECT Continent FROM countries) GROUP BY f.ContId ORDER BY f.ContId ASC
SELECT MakeId, Model FROM car_names LIMIT 4
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ContId), ContId FROM continents WHERE ContId BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR ContId NOT IN (SELECT Continent FROM countries AS y WHERE y.CountryId BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  y.Continent != 54)
SELECT COUNT(Id), AVG(Accelerate), COUNT(DISTINCT MPG) FROM cars_data WHERE Weight < 3400;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Cylinders) FROM cars_data WHERE Accelerate != 56 GROUP BY Id
SELECT AVG(d.Id), COUNT(DISTINCT d.Country) FROM car_makers AS d WHERE  d.Id <= 41
SELECT Make, COUNT(DISTINCT Model) FROM car_names WHERE MakeId <= 28 GROUP BY Make;
SELECT car_makers.Maker FROM car_makers AS p JOIN car_makers ON car_makers.Id = p.Id ORDER BY car_makers.Maker DESC
SELECT MakeId FROM car_names WHERE  MakeId >= 99 ORDER BY MakeId DESC

SELECT a.Year, cars_data.Edispl, cars_data.Year FROM cars_data AS a JOIN cars_data ON cars_data.Id = a.Id WHERE  a.Year >= 64 GROUP BY cars_data.Year HAVING MIN(a.Weight) = 53 ORDER BY cars_data.Year DESC LIMIT 9
SELECT e.Model FROM model_list AS e WHERE e.Maker BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  e.Maker <= 95
SELECT j.CountryId, j.CountryName FROM countries AS j WHERE  j.CountryId > 68 ORDER BY j.CountryName DESC
SELECT car_names.MakeId, model_list.Maker FROM car_names JOIN car_makers ON car_names.MakeId = car_makers.Id JOIN model_list ON car_makers.Id = model_list.Maker ORDER BY car_names.MakeId ASC LIMIT 8
SELECT CountryId FROM countries WHERE CountryId BETWEEN 1 AND 10 ORDER BY CountryId DESC LIMIT 3

SELECT COUNT(cars_data.Edispl), model_list.Maker, AVG(cars_data.Weight), cars_data.Cylinders FROM model_list JOIN car_names ON car_names.Model = model_list.Model AND car_names.MakeId = model_list.Maker JOIN cars_data ON cars_data.Id = car_names.MakeId WHERE cars_data.Edispl != 33 GROUP BY cars_data.Cylinders HAVING AVG(cars_data.Weight) > 67 LIMIT 5
SELECT MAX(h.Id), h.Id, h.FullName, h.Maker FROM car_makers AS h WHERE FullName IN (SELECT FullName FROM car_makers WHERE  Id > 32) GROUP BY h.Maker, h.Id, h.FullName HAVING MAX(h.Id) > 31
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT k.Make), k.MakeId FROM car_names AS k WHERE  k.MakeId != 38 LIMIT 8
